        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This method schedules the port with the receiver. You can add a port to multiple input modes. When the receiver is running in the specified mode, it dispatches messages destined for that port to the port’s designated handler routine. "
